
🏨 Hotel Booking Frontend - React Project

This is a fully responsive frontend hotel booking interface built using React.js. It allows users to explore rooms, check availability, and view essential details with a clean and user-friendly design.

🚀 Features
- Beautiful landing page with navigation
- Room listing with images and descriptions
- Responsive layout for mobile and desktop
- React Router-based navigation
- Organized component structure
- Clean UI with reusable components

📁 Folder Structure
React-projects/
└── hotel/
    ├── public/
    ├── src/
    │   ├── components/
    │   ├── pages/
    │   └── App.js
    ├── package.json
    └── README.txt

🛠️ Installation and Running the Project

Make sure you have Node.js and npm installed on your machine.

1. Navigate to the project folder:
   cd hotel

2. Install dependencies:
   npm install

3. Start the development server:
   npm start

The app will run on http://localhost:3000

👨‍💻 Developer Notes

This project is a part of my Frontend Developer portfolio and is focused on React.js development only. Backend/API integration is not included in this repository.

